trans-unit.source: An error occurred. The information "%s" is missing.
trans-unit.target: Nisy hadisoana niseho. Tsy ampy ny fampahafantarana "%s".

trans-unit.source: An error occurred. The template "%s" is missing.
trans-unit.target: Nisy hadisoana niseho. Tsy ao ny lasitra "%s".

trans-unit.source: Cannot write images for this type: %1$s. Please check the %2$s folder's writing permissions.
trans-unit.target: Tsy afaka manoratra ny sary hoan'ito karazana: %1$s. Jereo aza fady ny fahazoana alalana manoratra hoan'ny dosie %2$s.

trans-unit.source: Current theme is unavailable. Please check your theme's directory name ("%s") and permissions.
trans-unit.target: Tsy misy ao ny themenao amin'izao. Jereo aza fady ny anaran'ny dosie misy ny theme-nao ("%s") sy ny fahazoany alalana.
Tsy nety ny fanovana ny haben'ny fisie sary (%filepath%)
Tsy mety ny endriky ny fisie.

trans-unit.source: Original image is corrupt (%filename%) for product ID %id% or bad permission on folder.
trans-unit.target: Ratsy ny sary tany am-boalohany (%filename%) an'ny ID entana %id% na fahazoana alalana ratsy amin'ny dosie.

trans-unit.source: Original image is missing or empty (%filename%) for product ID %id%
trans-unit.target: Tsy ao ny sary tany am-boalohany na foana (%filename%) hoan'ny ID entana %id%

trans-unit.source: Source file does not exist or is empty (%filepath%)
trans-unit.target: Tsy misy ny fisie iandohana na tsy misy n'inon'inona (%filepath%)

trans-unit.source: The page Category cannot be moved here.
trans-unit.target: Tsy azo afindra eto ny pejy Sokajy.

trans-unit.source: Your theme has been correctly exported: %path%
trans-unit.target: Tafaondrana araka ny tokony ho izy ny theme-nao: %path%
